MT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/australias-famous-twelve-apostles-landmark-rose-out-of-the-sea-across-missions-of-years-180988715/</guid></item><item><title>1969 年，披头士乐队进行了最后一场演出。他们在伦敦的临时屋顶舞台很快将成为博物馆</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/in-1969-the-beatles-played-one-final-show-their-makeshift-rooftop-stage-in-london-will-soon-become-a-museum-180988714/</link><description>来到萨维尔街 3 号的游客将能够看到重建的地下录音室，披头士乐队在那里制作了他们的最后一张专辑《Let It Be》，并站在屋顶上，乐队在那里为伦敦人带来了一场惊喜的音乐会</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 May 2026 18:40:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/in-1969-the-beatles-played-one-final-show-their-makeshift-rooftop-stage-in-london-will-soon-become-a-museum-180988714/</guid></item><item><title>查看赢得德国自然摄影协会年度竞赛的 15 张令人惊叹的照片</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/see-15-stunning-images-that-won-the-german-society-for-nature-photographys-annual-contest-180988711/</link><description>从猛冲的青蛙到企鹅的雄伟动作，这些获奖照片捕捉到了野生动物的奇迹和自然景观的美丽</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 May 2026 14:42:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/see-15-stunning-images-that-won-the-german-society-for-nature-photographys-annual-contest-180988711/</guid></item><item><title>美国宇航局好奇号火星车的手臂上卡了一块火星岩石好几天。看着它最终把顽固的石头抖掉</title><link>https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/nasas-curiosity-rover-had-a-martian-rock-stuck-on-its-arm-for-days-watch-it-successfully-shook-the-stubborn-stone-off-180988708/</link><description>据航天局称，虽然钻探使岩石破裂，但这是该仪器第一次意外地从地面拉出整块岩石</description><pubDate>Mon, 11 May 2026 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.smithsonianmag.com/smart-news/nasas-curiosity-rover-had-a-martian-rock-stuck-on-its-arm-for-days-watch-it-successfully-shook-the-stubborn-stone-off-180988708/</guid></item></channel></rss>